# ===========================================
# PCD Training App - Environment Variables
# ===========================================

# PocketBase URL - used by the frontend to connect to PocketBase API
# In production, this should point to the Apache proxy (e.g., https://training-hub.ku.ac.ae)
# In development, point to local PocketBase (e.g., http://127.0.0.1:8090)
# PocketBase is deployed as a separate service
VITE_POCKETBASE_URL=http://your-pocketbase-url:8090

# === Auto-Provisioning ===
# SSO users are automatically created in PocketBase on first login
# New users get role='user' by default
# Admins must be assigned manually via Team Roles tab in admin portal
# See docs/INFRA.md for details on user provisioning flow

# ===========================================
# Deployment Architecture (Coolify)
# ===========================================
# 
# Service 1: PocketBase
# - Image: ghcr.io/pocketbase/pocketbase:latest
# - Port: 8090
# - Requires GitHub Container Registry credentials in Coolify settings
#
# Service 2: PCD App
# - Built from Dockerfile
# - Port: 8022
# - Build arg: VITE_POCKETBASE_URL points to PocketBase service
#
# Services are deployed separately on Coolify.
# ===========================================
